        "official_intent_excerpt": "Big boards equal big guy fun! Ben Aipa’s staple longboard, The Big Brother Sting is a high-performance tank designed to power through the mushiest of conditions. Extra thickness in the center of the board with a nicely foiled rail gives the perfect...",
        "source_scope": "official_manufacturer_canonical_evidence"
